49
00:02:33,528 --> 00:02:35,488
I think she was my Uber driver.

50
00:02:36,114 --> 00:02:37,907
I hope you gave her a five-star rating.

51
00:02:37,991 --> 00:02:39,784
Cooper, what are you doing?

52
00:02:39,868 --> 00:02:42,203
Making up for lost time.
What does it matter to you?

53
00:02:42,287 --> 00:02:46,374
This is the first time you spent the night
at our house since you split from Billie.

54
00:02:46,457 --> 00:02:49,419
- You got a random teenager with you.
- Okay.

55
00:02:49,502 --> 00:02:50,503
She's in college.

56
00:02:50,587 --> 00:02:54,007
