57
00:02:56,801 --> 00:02:59,220
You remember Francesca,
your "alleged" girlfriend?

58
00:03:00,138 --> 00:03:02,724
I've never met her before
but she texted me last night repeatedly

59
00:03:02,807 --> 00:03:05,244
saying she hadn't heard from you in days
and was worried sick.

60
00:03:05,268 --> 00:03:07,562
- Shit.
- I covered for you,

61
00:03:07,645 --> 00:03:09,522
but you introduced her to your kids.

62
00:03:09,606 --> 00:03:10,857
What happened?

63
00:03:13,651 --> 00:03:15,028
I had a run-in with Billie.

64
00:03:16,321 --> 00:03:18,114
A couple, actually.

65
00:03:19,949 --> 00:03:21,659
Cooper, you need to take time

66
00:03:21,743 --> 00:03:24,037
to deal with the emotional fallout
from your split.

67
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,955
- I am.
- No, you're not.

68
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:28,499
You walked out on Billie
and ran straight to Francesca,

69
00:03:28,583 --> 00:03:30,919
and you jumped in with both feet
on the same night.

70
00:03:31,002 --> 00:03:32,295
Divorce is a huge loss.

71
00:03:32,378 --> 00:03:34,589
- It's like a death.
- A death I wanted.

72
00:03:34,672 --> 00:03:37,050
Everything I'm doing now is what I want.

73
00:03:37,133 --> 00:03:38,885
Maybe for the first time in my life.

74
00:03:38,968 --> 00:03:41,512
I did the whole
"sex is a salve for your problems" thing,

75
00:03:41,596 --> 00:03:44,515
it works great for 15 minutes,
you feel like the hottest guy.

76
00:03:44,599 --> 00:03:46,684
You forget how much
you fucking hate yourself.

77
00:03:46,768 --> 00:03:48,519
No, I hate her. Not me.

78
00:03:48,603 --> 00:03:52,023
Mm-hm. You've never hated anyone.
You've never had a reason to.

79
00:03:52,106 --> 00:03:54,192
Which means you've lived
a pretty charmed life.

80
00:03:54,275 --> 00:03:57,362
It also means now that things
aren't going exactly according to plan,

81
00:03:57,445 --> 00:03:58,905
you don't know how to process.

82
00:04:00,031 --> 00:04:04,535
I always knew some good would come out
of being a miserable, closeted gay kid

83
00:04:04,619 --> 00:04:06,579
in uber-heteronormative '90s Connecticut.

84
00:04:06,663 --> 00:04:08,331
It was fucking traumatizing.

85
00:04:08,831 --> 00:04:10,458
But I dealt with my shit

86
00:04:10,541 --> 00:04:13,253
so I could show up
for the rest of my life, including Brett.

87
00:04:13,336 --> 00:04:14,337
Good for you.

88
00:04:15,421 --> 00:04:17,548
Whatever you're going through,
just go through it.

89
00:04:18,132 --> 00:04:19,759
Come out the other end like I did.

90
00:04:20,843 --> 00:04:23,429
Try to minimize collateral damage.

91
00:04:23,513 --> 00:04:25,682
It's not fair
to drag Francesca down with you.

92
00:04:28,226 --> 00:04:33,982
Okay, honey, I am gonna miss you so much.

93
00:04:34,065 --> 00:04:35,692
But I hope you have fun with Daddy.

94
00:04:35,775 --> 00:04:38,861
Daddy said he's taking us for sledding
and hot chocolate.

95
00:04:38,945 --> 00:04:39,945
He did?

96
00:04:40,822 --> 00:04:41,823
That's great.

97
00:04:41,906 --> 00:04:45,952
Yoo-hoo! Carpool's arrived.

98
00:04:46,035 --> 00:04:47,453
Do you like my tiara?

99
00:04:47,537 --> 00:04:50,957
It is my birthday tiara
and I'm going to wear it all day

100
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:53,126
even at my Manhattan spa party.

101
00:04:53,209 --> 00:04:54,544
Are you as excited as I am?

102
00:04:54,627 --> 00:04:58,339
Caroline, I am so sorry,
I don't think I'll be able to make it.

103
00:04:58,423 --> 00:05:00,925
It's been a crazy few days.

104
00:05:01,009 --> 00:05:04,512
Well, Hudson, why don't you
go jump in the car with Hannah,

105
00:05:04,595 --> 00:05:06,389
and I will be right there.

106
00:05:06,472 --> 00:05:07,472
Okay.

107
00:05:07,765 --> 00:05:09,309
- Bye.
- Bye, sweetheart.

108
00:05:14,063 --> 00:05:17,025
I know what happened
with Cooper and Trina.

109
00:05:17,108 --> 00:05:22,697
And I think that you and Trina need to
talk it out in a relaxed environment.

110
00:05:23,281 --> 00:05:24,657
Like a spa.

111
00:05:24,741 --> 00:05:27,618
- No.
- You can't avoid each other forever.

112
00:05:27,702 --> 00:05:29,203
Not in Greenwich, anyway.

113
00:05:29,954 --> 00:05:32,665
Besides... it's my birthday

114
00:05:32,749 --> 00:05:35,543
