there to celebrate me.

115
00:05:36,294 --> 00:05:39,088
Pretty, pretty, pretty, please.

116
00:05:39,172 --> 00:05:40,298
Okay, fine.

117
00:05:40,381 --> 00:05:41,381
Yay!

118
00:05:41,758 --> 00:05:45,928
Oh, P.S., I saw the news this morning
about your sexy ex.

119
00:05:46,012 --> 00:05:48,181
It's so sad what's happening to him.

120
00:05:48,264 --> 00:05:49,515
What are you talking about?

121
00:05:49,599 --> 00:05:50,767
The lawsuit.

122
00:05:50,850 --> 00:05:52,018
What?

123
00:05:52,101 --> 00:05:53,227
Oh.

124
00:05:57,899 --> 00:06:00,693
I mean, at least it's a nice picture.

125
00:06:00,777 --> 00:06:03,613
He is so photogenic.

126
00:06:09,494 --> 00:06:11,788
Sash, what's with the getup?

127
00:06:12,538 --> 00:06:15,708
This is what it's like when you're
top of Twitter's 10 Most Hated.

128
00:06:15,792 --> 00:06:18,753
One second I'm talking
about Kam's magic penis

129
00:06:18,836 --> 00:06:20,505
and the next, I'm anti-feminist?

130
00:06:20,588 --> 00:06:22,548
It's ridiculous but it'll blow over.

131
00:06:22,632 --> 00:06:25,343
- It's a 60-second news cycle these days.
- Yeah.

132
00:06:25,426 --> 00:06:29,680
And, hey, at least
I'm not being sued for $450 million.

133
00:06:29,764 --> 00:06:30,973
Oh, my God. Right?

134
00:06:31,057 --> 00:06:32,558
I still can't believe it.

135
00:06:33,392 --> 00:06:36,604
I mean, I'm sure Brad's totally innocent.

136
00:06:36,687 --> 00:06:38,356
