00:46:45,677 --> 00:46:48,180
Is this Gigi Everett's room?
I'm Brad Simon, the father.

766
00:46:48,263 --> 00:46:50,224
Hang on. You gotta put on a gown.

767
00:46:50,307 --> 00:46:51,907
[Billie] <i>...will never feel right again.</i>

768
00:46:52,976 --> 00:46:54,228
<i>At least not for you.</i>

769
00:46:59,483 --> 00:47:00,817
<i>So be sure...</i>

770
00:47:02,486 --> 00:47:04,154
<i>when you make that choice...</i>

771
00:47:06,323 --> 00:47:07,824
<i>you're willing to follow through.</i>

772
00:47:07,908 --> 00:47:08,908
[both moaning]

773
00:47:16,583 --> 00:47:18,418
[screaming]

774
00:47:19,795 --> 00:47:21,547
I'm so sorry I'm late.

775
00:47:21,630 --> 00:47:23,257
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

776
00:47:23,340 --> 00:47:24,424
[sobbing]

777
00:47:26,718 --> 00:47:28,554
I kept trying to reach you.

778
00:47:28,637 --> 00:47:31,223
- Why didn't you pick up?
- I'm so sorry.

779
00:47:31,306 --> 00:47:32,391
I'm sorry, okay?

780
00:47:35,602 --> 00:47:39,314
But I'm here now. Hey, I'm here. I'm here.

781
00:47:39,398 --> 00:47:41,108
[doctor] Okay, here we go.

782
00:47:41,191 --> 00:47:42,109
You're ready.

783
00:47:42,192 --> 00:47:44,194
You can do this. Hey.

784
00:47:44,278 --> 00:47:45,278
You got this.

785
00:47:48,699 --> 00:47:49,950
Push.

786
00:47:52,244 --> 00:47:53,328
[doctor] Push, Gigi.

787
00:47:54,162 --> 00:47:55,162
Oh, my God.

788
00:47:55,914 --> 00:47:57,749
He's coming. He's coming.

789
00:47:58,792 --> 00:47:59,792
He's coming.

790
00:48:01,712 --> 00:48:06,383
<i>♪ Spent your life collecting
So you can never forget ♪</i>

791
00:48:09,094 --> 00:48:10,429
[doctor] Congratulations.

792
00:48:10,512 --> 00:48:14,600
<i>♪ Treasured moments
Become lost treasures ♪</i>

793
00:48:14,683 --> 00:48:18,437
<i>♪ When you can't recollect ♪</i>

794
00:48:19,771 --> 00:48:23,400
<i>♪ Everyone keeps asking are we okay ♪</i>

795
00:48:24,109 --> 00:48:28,822
<i>♪ The truth is we're not
But I don't know what to say ♪</i>

796
00:48:28,905 --> 00:48:31,074
[vocalizing]

797
00:48:51,428 --> 00:48:53,221
[Billie] <i>Because if you choose wrong...</i>

798
00:48:55,140 --> 00:48:57,768
<i>be prepared to live
with the consequences...</i>

799
00:48:59,645 --> 00:49:00,645
<i>forever.</i>

800
00:49:03,148 --> 00:49:05,984
[theme music playing]

